        "text_iicg9N": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For those who love the warmth of gold with exceptional value, our <strong>gold vermeil jewellery </strong>is the perfect choice. We use a thick layer of <strong>18-carat gold (3 microns thick) </strong>over <strong>solid sterling silver</strong>, offering a rich, long-lasting finish. Unlike gold-plated jewellery, gold vermeil contains no base metals like brass or copper, making it a superior choice for sensitive skin.<br/></p>",
