        "heading_wc4nY6": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will Vermeil Wear Out?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_RpyMft": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Vermeil <a href=\"https://www.lilyblanche.com/collections/jewellery\" title=\"https://www.lilyblanche.com/collections/jewellery\">Jewellery</a> is Built to last. Lily Blanche exceeds industry standards with 18 carat gold at a minimum of 3 microns, significantly more than the legal 2.5 micron requirement. </p><p>Store your Lily Blanche Pieces in our Intercept anti-tarnish pouches, included with every Lily Blanche Jewellery Care Kit. Custom made for us in the USA, the pouches are woven with patented polymers to neutralise the gasses that cause tarnishing. </p><p>Vermeil jewellery represents an outstanding and affordable alternative to solid gold. Its sterling silver foundation—a pure precious metal—makes it an excellent option for those with metal sensitivities. For those seeking to elevate their jewellery collection, vermeil offers exceptional value and quality.</p><p></p>"
          }
        }
      },
