    "rich_text_MFNeam": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_JH8Pxh": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_LnX8Hm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Each gemstone is carefully set by skilled artisans, ensuring lasting beauty and durability.</p><p>As natural gemstones, ours will often contain small inclusions. far from a flaw, these are the marker of the gemstone's unique identity, gemmologists use them to confirm that stone is natural rather than synthetic. Whilst inclusions in diamonds are often seen negatively, in coloured gemstones they are often prized as a sign of authentication. You can read more about inclusions here.</p><p>We do not use any lab-created stones in our jewellery.</p><p>You can read more about the origins and properties of our <a href=\"/pages/birthstones-by-month\" title=\"Birthstones By Month\">precious gemstone jewellery here.</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "button_U3AM7e": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop all gemstone jewellery",
            "button_link": "https://www.lilyblanche.com/collections/gemstones",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "button_label_2": "",
            "button_link_2": "",
            "button_style_secondary_2": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
