    "rich_text_gzU4kY": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_JDacRe": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Transparency",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_yM7gag": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We aim to provide as much transparency as possible to our customers. All dimensions and weights listed in the product descriptions and details boxes include the entire jewellery piece, including pendant and locket bails (the loops that chains pass through) and earring wires. The item weight refers to the locket or pendant component only, while the total weight includes the full piece with the chain.</p><p>We are always happy to answer any questions about jewellery dimensions or materials. Please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@lilyblanche.com\">hello@lilyblanche.com </a>or via our live chat.</p><p>Our jewellery is photographed in multiple ways to give the best representation. The initial image on a white background meets Google standards and is shot under bright studio lights. Model photography is taken in natural light, and videos are available on our website, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lilyblanchejewellery/\">Instagram</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lilyblanchejewellery\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@lily_blanche_jewellery\">TikTok, </a><a href=\"https://uk.pinterest.com/lilyblanchejewellery/\">Pinterest</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@LilyBlancheJewellery\">YouTube </a>to provide additional perspective.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_JDacRe",
        "text_yM7gag"
      ],
